title: Condo/Townhome in Greenwood Village
posting_body: ['Description', "Clean, Well-maintained, Light and Bright 1 Bedroom, 2 Bath, Loft Style condo in DTC, with 10' ceilings, beautiful, newly refinished hardwood floors, newly painted, stainless appliances, granite countertops, closet built-in, and washer dryer included.", 'Building has security features such as underground parking with automatic overhead garage door, so you can drive into the building and then go immediately to your elevator and into your unit, without ever going outside.', 'Beautiful grounds, close to Restaurants, Shopping, Light Rail, DTC offices.', 'Great access to I-25 and I-225, Downtown, DIA, etc.', 'Village Plaza Lofts', 'Features', 'Cable', 'Microwave', 'Hardwood floors', 'Air conditioner', 'Refrigerator', 'Dishwasher', 'Walk-in closets', 'Garage parking', 'Stove and oven', 'Private balcony', 'Dryer', 'Heat', 'Washer', 'Storage space', 'Carpet', 'Ceiling fan', 'Controlled access', 'Disposal', 'Mirrors', 'Climate control', 'Kitchen island', 'Tile floors', 'Vaulted ceiling', 'Window coverings', 'High speed internet', 'Elevator', 'Parking', 'Storage space', 'Pool', 'Fitness center', 'Club house', 'Garage', 'Gate', 'Jogging and walking trails', 'Media room', 'Multi-use room', 'TV lounge']
